data.meta_description: 121 likes, 1 comments - universitynewengland on September 25, 2023: "Every fall, the #UniversityofNewEngland community gathers to commemorate the legacy of President and Mrs. Bush as esteemed political and community leaders. The George and Barbara Bush Distinguished Lecture Series offers an intimate look into the experiences of those closest to the former president as they provide unique insights into presidential leadership and political history. All are welcome to attend! Visit the link in our bio for more information.".
